------------------------------------------------------------------
KEY LESSON
------------------------------------------------------------------

Repeating-key XOR is one of the most common beginner crypto
challenges. The key is almost always visible in the challenge
description. The decryption script is always the same three
lines: load hex with bytes.fromhex(), define the key as bytes,
then XOR each byte with key[i % len(key)]. Verify by checking
the known flag prefix appears at the start of the output.
